Interactive CV
Sep 23, 2011 to current
/python, /python/xhpy, /python/django, /js, /css, /js/mootools, /html5, /writing/cv

- Designed and built this online CV using Django, XHPy, mootools, and HTML5
- Implemented a tag similarity algorithm based upon the Expected Mutual Information Measure
- Used this algorithm to build a dynamic interface that moves blocks horizontally according to their relevance to user-selected tag filters
- Added views optimized for print and mobile media, as well as for browsers lacking JavaScript support
